docs.lead_paragraph: BARCELONA, Feb. 12.--Generalissimo Francisco Franco's judicial authorities in Catalonia are actively continuing their investigations into wholesale confiscations of this rich industrial region's wealth and the destruction or sabotage of its great textile mills, most of which had been converted by the Republicans [Loyalists] into warmaterial factories.
